text: Grentzingen is a former commune. It is found in the Haut-Rhin department of eastern France. On 1 January 2016, it was merged into the new commune of Illtal.Arrêté 17 December 2015 It is 25 km west of Basel and 10 km southeast of Altkirch. == References == Category:Former communes in Haut-Rhin Category:2016 disestablishments in France
title: Grentzingen
